=======

- Implemente a função `filter` usando foldr.

~~~~~{.haskell}
filter :: (a -> Bool) -> [a] -> [a]
filter _ [] = []
filter p (x : xs)
    | p x = x : filter p xs
    | otherwise = filter p xs
~~~~~

Exemplo
=======

- Implemente a função `filter` usando foldr.

~~~~~{.haskell}
filter :: (a -> Bool) -> [a] -> [a]
filter p = foldr step []
   where
     step x ac = if p x then x : ac else ac
~~~~~~~

